{"type": "article", "id": 46723, "title": "把手机交给台灯，这灯才答应亮起｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-10-31T23:36:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 45154, "name": "Bento Graphics"}, {"id": 45155, "name": "Stoft studio"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 181, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171101073623N2n5svwy7ahPeprJ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 15.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Tokyo Signs by Bento Graphics</h3><p>不喜欢随大流的旅行纪念品？你有没有考虑过把城市的视觉系统换一种方式带回家？来自日本东京的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://bentographics.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bento Graphics</a> 就以城市生活中常见的标识、霓虹灯以及广告灯等视觉元素为主题，创立了一个名为 Tokyo Signs 的服饰品牌。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://tokyosigns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174717Ocvq0rjmoaFeus9t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174717OmMPJ7DljS5wcbgI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174717NMrpXe7RfhHuZSiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.252000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ONO Roller by Ari Horowitz</h3><p>打着减压名号、让人们能够从小动作中解放的玩具越来越多，如果你平时喜欢转笔的话，美国设计师 Ari Horowitz 带来的 ONO Roller 可能比市面上的减压魔方更适合你。它单手就能掌握，触感和用手让掌心的两支马克笔反复旋转差不多。由于采用了航天级的铝合金，转起来顺畅无声不会吵到别人，滚轮结构意味着你也可以把它当迷你按摩器使用。通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/sleeklifedesign/ono-roller-relaxation-in-the-palm-of-your-hand\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 22 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174735hSKLk7HPOridp51A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614706\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174734MLYdHZUc2J9Kjvfb.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.554412\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174735gD1PJ4OR5dsfShjY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174734od7JmaxnTbPYs9D5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.356250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174734pAyjOPBJhubscEYf.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.477941\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Offline Lamp by Klemens Schillinger</h3><p>还记得那个<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/45973.html\">只有上交手机才能点亮的灯饰</a>吗？最近，奥地利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.klemensschillinger.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Klemens Schillinger</a> 也带来了一盏希望你戒断手机的台灯。和在饭局上玩“叠手机”比谁先放弃不同，Offline Lamp 更像是为工作了一天，想静下心来看本书的人设计的：它的底座是一个抽屉，只有放入手机并关上后，顶部的灯才会亮起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174757IYQhej6qHwkTLKBo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174757VnPesqZKglNdUzIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174757v7l0VrUKPNzZn1Wf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Whittle Away by Stoft studio</h3><p>在不久前举办的荷兰设计周上，埃因霍温举行了一场名为 What’s your DNA? 的展览，由三位瑞典设计师组成的工作室 <a href=\"http://www.stoft-studio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Stoft studio</a> 带来了借鉴传统工艺打造的木柜系列 Whittle Away。柜门表面经过特殊处理，看起来像是将树皮掀起一样，特意露出的部分则经过精心的上色，让人联想到排列有序的彩色铅笔。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174815DwPN8qXFbU4BROey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174815Vz1eaBJc8HYSQrsh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201710311748157RoC6vDrhwXUI1Ek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174815rB7zKsLm3G4tR8b1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Illustrated Marathon Course Maps by Cape Horn Illustration</h3><p>设计工作室 Cape Horn Illustration 的创始人 Phil Thompson 是一名现居芝加哥的插画师，热爱跑步的他经常绘制地图、跑步时发现的建筑或是不为人知的城市历史。在完成自己的第一场马拉松后，他决定根据自己日常跑步的路线，绘制一张特别的马拉松地图，让那些不参与比赛的人们能够从跑者的角度欣赏到地标建筑。自芝加哥之后，他又陆续绘制了纽约、波士顿、德国柏林和日本东京的地图。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.capehorn-illustration.com/collections/art_of_the_marathon\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价从 28 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174828uA5EbZMRCBIFTLOq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174828pdMAF01OBv8hNJoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174828TPiJVZHustGjdgRC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174828vbwnJD0KgeNiVh9o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.485333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Temescal Brewing by Beau Monroe</h3><p>位于加州奥克兰的啤酒厂 <a href=\"http://www.temescalbrewing.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Temescal Brewing</a> 每月都会推出一款月度啤酒，设计师 <a href=\"http://www.beaumonroe.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beau Monroe</a> 受邀为此打造了这套乍看之下有点乱，但却有某种统一美感的啤酒包装。从鲜艳明亮的用色不难看出 Monroe 的灵感来源于孟菲斯设计小组，而这种方格形式则借鉴了法国品牌 A.P.C 用回收布料拼成的被子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017103117493779e8ZlVfsiDjXhyz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174937ON1v6bSXinMzoFIG.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171031174937CTrPOQcb4Jl5AHon.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.457333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}